snippet.title: Workout AMBER HEARD «Aquaman»
snippet.description:
Aquaman (2018)
On the set 'Aquaman'

Film description: Arthur Curry learns that he is the heir to the underwater kingdom of Atlantis, and must step forward to lead his people and to be a hero to the world. 

Director: James Wan
Cast: Jason Momoa (Arthur Curry / Aquaman), Nicole Kidman (Queen Atlanna), Amber Heard (Mera), Dolph Lundgren (King Nereus), Willem Dafoe (Nuidis Vulko), Patrick Wilson (Orm / Ocean Master), Temuera Morrison (Thomas Curry), Yahya Abdul-Mateen II (Black Manta) ...
